title: Data Entry Clerk Work From Home - Part-Time Focus Group
description:
Are you a customer service agent looking to supplement your current income? Then we have what you want. We're looking for folks in the Customer Service Agent industry who want to earn extra income working from home.


Job Requirements  Apply at:  http://www.abnhire.com


Here's what you need to get started:

• You'll need a laptop OR

• PC/MAC OR

• Smart device

• Stable internet connection

• At least 5 to 10 hours weekly availability

• Willingness to follow directions to the T

• Desire to follow through Here's what you'd be doing to make extra money from home

• Giving your feedback on Fortune 500 companies

• Sending emails, reviewing products, writing reviews

• Using your Customer Service skills as needed


Apply at:  http://www.abnhire.com


This is an entry-level gig, no experience is required, but we do train so you'll learn what's required to start making money.


Apply at:  http://www.abnhire.com
